 1萬元  共計    100萬元 4萬3,200元","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHV/109%2c%e9%87%8d%e8%a8%b4%2c3%2c20210127%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHV,109,重訴,3,20210127,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"重訴","JNO":"3","JDATE":"20210127","JTITLE":"侵權行為損害賠償"}